# Chaza – Real-Time Messaging Android App

## Overview
Chaza is a real-time messaging Android application built using Firebase Authentication and Firestore, enabling users to send and receive messages instantly.

## Features
- User authentication (signup/login)
- Real-time messaging using Firestore
- Multi-user chat support
- Persistent message storage

## Tech Stack
- Kotlin
- Firebase Authentication
- Firebase Firestore Database

## Challenges Faced
- Handling real-time message synchronization
- Preventing duplicate messages due to multiple listeners
- Managing UI updates efficiently

## Key Logic
Implemented real-time listeners with controlled updates to ensure consistent message delivery without duplication.
